## 3.4. Define the maximum number of samples to extract {#sec-max-samples}

:::: {.columns}

::: {.column width=0.3}



::: {#f910f3e8 .cell execution_count=19}

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=19}
![](cellpose_tutorial_files/figure-html/cell-20-output-1.png){}
